title: Neverland Solitaire v1.0.0 Android
description:
Neverland Solitaire v1.0.0 
Requirements: 2.2+
Overview: Take a trip to Neverland in this challenging and beautiful card matching and brain teaser game! 
Image

Alice invites you to Neverland this time. Clear the cards off the board by matching two cards of the same rank regardless the suit. Prove your attentiveness in the brain and puzzle game levels. Enjoy and play along with Alice in this exciting multilevel skill game with great graphics and sound effects!

This app has no advertisements
